{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339600/extras/dicegif.gif?t=1737138716\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>HO-HOP!</strong> is a fun Christmas board game that will bring holiday cheer to your evening! Designed for 1-4 players, this game lets you compete with friends as you race across a board filled with surprises and challenges. Each player takes turns rolling the dice, moving their character forward by the number shown. But watch out: some spaces will push you ahead, others will send you back, and special spaces with cards bring random buffs and debuffs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339600/extras/cardsgif.gif?t=1737138716\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game\u2019s surprise cards add an unpredictable twist: some players get boosts, while others find themselves stuck. There are spaces that make you skip turns, return to start, or face other obstacles on the way to victory. Your character will be pushed forward and pulled back on this wild journey. Only the player who can overcome all obstacles and reach the finish line first will be the winner!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>HO-HOP!</strong> is an unforgettable mix of luck, strategy, and Christmas magic!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Merry Christmas","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3339600/770861b9df0aedfc0c657cf806a4bce41bbdd0b0.jpg"},{"name":"Holly Jolly Win","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3339600/770861b9df0aedfc0c657cf806a4bce41bbdd0b0.jpg"}],"total":2},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3339600/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737138716","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstati